text: Came down to for UOB disney plushie redemption. Doesnt look like much of a “Short Q” to me. Waited for at least 30mins

Visited on 30/3

The reviews speak for itself.
True customer service should not be making your customers wait when you are unsure of your policy and require quite some time to check.
The service attitude of the younger guy at the counter was pleasant, but I think the older guy showed quite a but of unpleasant attitude.

Update on Thursday, 12 December 2024
Queue is moving fast at opening 11am. Came here to redeem our free Samsonite duffel bag, courtesy of Chubb Insurance/Amex Platinum.

Short queue during a weekday afternoon.
Got my stuff around 10-15 mins.
2nd time here; first time was a long long wait.

The staff not the best. The q not clear. They just let ppl that queue and left, come back and go to the front again, even if there’s others that arrive alr. No q pole, no queue management. Only after we queue at where we think is right after a few minutes then they tell us we queue wrongly, need to queue all the way from the back when there were new customers, twice. Imagine asking us to requeue twice from the back just cause they didn’t share where the proper queue.

Also they won’t provide bags. Please bring your own.
